data.title: International Black Nobel Prize Winners
data.meta_description: Digital image of poster depicting Black Nobel prize winners. The poster was produced by the Historical Research Repository and has a 1993 date. Depicted on the poster are: Ralph Johnson Bunche, Rev. Martin Luther King, Jr., Toni Morrison, Albert John Luthuli, Bishop Desmond Mpilo Tutu, Sir William Arthur Lewis, Derek Walcott and Wole Soyinka.
